Best for video background music Chill Trap Hip Hop(837066)

texts.content: {"text":"Maritime transport accounts for more than 30% of\nCO2 emissions in the transport industry.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/Dell PC/AppData/Local/CapCut/Apps/6.1.0.2329/Resources/Font/SystemFont/en.ttf","id":""},"size":5,"range":[0,89]}]}

{"text":"In Chile, it's characterized by high fuel consumption \nand low efficiency. This could change now.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/Dell PC/AppData/Local/CapCut/Apps/6.1.0.2329/Resources/Font/SystemFont/en.ttf","id":""},"size":5,"range":[0,97]}]}

{"text":"Tugboats play a fundamental role in the maneuvering\nof ships in ports, rivers, and open seas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/Dell PC/AppData/Local/CapCut/Apps/6.1.0.2329/Resources/Font/SystemFont/en.ttf","id":""},"size":5,"range":[0,93]}]}

{"text":"But their diesel propulsion systems operate 
in highly inefficient conditions, 

operating at low power outputs for extended periods,

 resulting in excessive fuel consumption and high emissions.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/Dell PC/AppData/Local/CapCut/Apps/6.1.0.2329/Resources/Font/SystemFont/en.ttf","id":""},"size":5,"range":[0,195]}]}

{"text":"The AC3E, together with the UACh, promotes 
energy-efficient technologies, 
including hybrid ship propulsion
and charge infrastructure in ports","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/Dell PC/AppData/Local/CapCut/Apps/6.1.0.2329/Resources/Font/SystemFont/en.ttf","id":""},"size":5,"range":[0,143]}]}

{"text":"The objective of this work is to design and dimension\nan energy storage system for a hybrid tugboat,\nadapted to its current operating profile.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/Dell PC/AppData/Local/CapCut/Apps/6.1.0.2329/Resources/Font/SystemFont/en.ttf","id":""},"size":5,"range":[0,142]}]}

{"text":"The goal is to improve energy efficiency and 
reduce fuel consumption and polluting emissions.

(Animation: Hybrid engine system with
 diesel and battery componentes working together)","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/Dell PC/AppData/Local/CapCut/Apps/6.1.0.2329/Resources/Font/SystemFont/en.ttf","id":""},"size":5,"range":[0,183]}]}

{"text":"Depending on the operating mode (standby or towing), \nthe system can switch power sources, \nimproving overall efficiency by 10% to 30%.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/Dell PC/AppData/Local/CapCut/Apps/6.1.0.2329/Resources/Font/SystemFont/en.ttf","id":""},"size":5,"range":[0,135]}]}

{"text":"As with electric vehicles, the core of this innovation is
the battery. Several technologies were considered:
LFP, LTO, and NMC, each evaluated for its
performance under real-world tugboat load profiles, 
in addition to other technical and economic considerations.

(Visual: Battery comparison chart, load profile graph, 
and simple battery equations)","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/Dell PC/AppData/Local/CapCut/Apps/6.1.0.2329/Resources/Font/SystemFont/en.ttf","id":""},"size":5,"range":[0,350]}]}

{"text":"A zero-order Shepherd model was used to simulate
battery behavior, which helped design a complete 
battery bank and integrate it into 
the tug's propulsion system.","styles":[{"size":5,"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,163]}]}

{"text":"This information is relevant to consider when integrating \nthe different elements of the tug's powertrain\ninto the simulation to meet its various technical requirements.","styles":[{"size":5,"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,169]}]}

{"text":"The design of a battery bank for a tugboat is the basis 
for the design of the hybrid propulsion system. 
This increases the complexity and accuracy of simulations,
 which allow the generation of
 experimental test scenarios that bring 
this proposal closer to reality.

(Visual: Cleaner ports, animated emission reductions,
hybrid tug in action)","styles":[{"size":5,"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"range":[0,346]}]}
